<div style="height:20px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><strong>Paste the Link &amp; Download</strong></p>



<p class="has-text-align-center">Paste the link into the &#8220;Paste a video URL&#8221; field, then click <strong>Download</strong>.</p>
